OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe winds
OL,6,Feasing and the showers becoming well
OL,7,Fscattered this evening. Dry of a time
OL,8,Fovernight, but thickening cloud and
OL,9,Fpatchy rain later as winds turn into
OL,10,Fthe southwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with patchy
OL,13,Flight rain and drizzle at first, but
OL,14,Fbecoming mostly dry. Best of any
OL,15,Fbrightness across Orkney. Moderate to
OL,16,Ffresh southwest winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
