OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FOutbreaks of rain gradually clearing
OL,7,Fsouth on Wednesday and windy at times.
OL,8,FRain or showers on Thursday and
OL,9,FFriday, which may be heavy. Winds
OL,10,Fstrengthening on Friday, gales
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
